M|felix|- **Revenue model:** Fashion DTC (transactional — each sale must be re-acquired)
M|felix|- **Key revenue lever:** AOV (Average Order Value) — price mix and upsell drive this
M|felix|- **Seasonality:** December typically 2x baseline — do not model as trend signal
M|felix|- **Margin benchmark:** Fashion e-commerce gross margin target 40–60%
M|felix|- **ROAS threshold:** < 3x → pause paid cg, diagnose before scaling
M|felix|- Product launch spikes are not trend signals — always separate launch revenue from baseline
M|felix|- Repeat purchase rate is a leading indicator of brand health, not just a retention metric
M|felix|- Inventory costs are often underestimated — include warehousing + returns in COGS model
M|felix|- Influencer partnership ROI lags 4–6 weeks — do not attribute revenue to cg week
